Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.99,0:13:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說 這…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.63,0:13:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不就是私闖女生房間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:13:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是犯罪！
