Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有 請叫我Kleist…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連硬盤整個帶走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會暴露的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那怎辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之讓我看可疑的數據 竹山
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.52,0:16:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我Kleist
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:16:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學生名單？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NPC…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.76,0:17:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我們也在裡面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.53,0:17:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那只是份名單吧
