Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.28,0:17:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佯動班被制壓了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.50,0:17:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天使回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次也毫無收穫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.53,0:17:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們撤退吧
