Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.86,0:18:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.16,0:19:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竹山
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.91,0:19:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 請叫我Kleist
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的人生
